				<p class="lead">At Coder Factory, we all <em>love</em> what we do.</p>
				<p>Creating technology is an empowering pursuit that has the potential to improve the lives of people everywhere. <strong>We want more women to have the opportunity to love working in the tech industry.</strong></p>

				
			</div></div>

			<div class="thumbnail">
